'''飓风阿尔玛'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Alma}}）是[[1962年大西洋飓风季|1962年大西洋飓风季]]首场获命名的风暴，比[[1941年大西洋飓风季|1941年]]后各大西洋飓风季首场风暴的形成日期都要晚，源自8月26日[[南佛罗里达|南佛罗里达]]近海的[[东风波|东风波]]。成为热带低气压后，气旋从南佛罗里达[[登陆_(气象学)|上岸]]，佛罗里达州降下小雨，近海波涛汹涌，整体所受影响很小。8月27日清晨，热带低气压回到大西洋，于当天增强成热带风暴并获名“阿尔玛”。风暴接下来沿[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]近海向东北移动，于8月28日在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]近海强化成飓风。北卡罗莱纳州东部有电线杆被狂风刮倒，导致停电，该州的经济损失数额约为3.5万美元{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有损失数额均为1962年[[美元|美元]]价值。|group="注"}}。[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]还在部分地点引起[[海蚀|侵蚀]]。

气旋继续强化，于8月29日达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]155公里的最高强度，在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属二级飓风{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。不过，阿尔玛当天又在经过[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]近海期间减弱成一级飓风。风暴外围[[雨带|雨带]]产生狂风和降雨，海上波涛汹涌，[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]情况特别突出。新英格兰此前正逢旱灾，所以飓风产生的降水颇具助益。马萨诸塞州因狂风导致部分地点停电，电话服务中断。该州近海有上百艘船因海况恶劣被毁。新英格兰的损失数额不足100万美元。飓风蜿蜒向东行进，于9月30日在大西洋西北部弱化成热带风暴，最终于数小时后在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]南面转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Alma 1962 track.png}}
8月14日，[[电视红外观测卫星|电视红外观测卫星]]在东大西洋发现带有弱环流的东风波<ref name="mwr">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205905/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1962.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1962.pdf | title = The Hurricane Season of 1962 | deadurl = no | author = Gordon E. Dunn | date = 1963-04 | work = [[美国国家气象局|United States Weather Bureau Office Miami, Florida]] | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | pages = 202–203 | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref><ref name="stormdata">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170208132154/https://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-FCA94C42-9AF7-471C-8E18-0FEC2B3B9135.pdf | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-FCA94C42-9AF7-471C-8E18-0FEC2B3B9135.pdf | title = Storm Data: August 1962 | author = Luther Hodges | date = 1961 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2017-02-08 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。系统向西移动，于8月18日被科研飞机发现。四天后，系统进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]，整体结构依旧杂乱无章。东风波于8月24日经过[[古巴|古巴]]东部，再于次日进入[[佛罗里达海峡|佛罗里达海峡]]。<ref name="mwr" />接下来系统终于开始组织，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月26日中午12点在佛罗里达州东南近海发展成热带低气压。不久，气旋以持续风速每小时45公里强度从[[博卡拉顿|博卡拉顿]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。系统在距海岸线不远的陆地上行进，于8月27日清晨从[[匹尔斯堡_(佛罗里达州)|匹尔斯堡]]附近返回大西洋。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>气旋向东北移动，并在[[反气旋|反气旋]]影响下增强<ref name="mwr" />，于当天在佛罗里达州和[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]边界以东约240公里洋面强化成热带风暴并获名“阿尔玛”（{{lang|en|Alma}}）<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="mwr" />。

风暴沿[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]海岸线平行移动并稳步增强，于8月28日在北卡罗莱纳州[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）近海成为飓风<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="mwr" />，在此期间最低[[气压|气压]]降至986[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.1[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}8月29日早上6点，阿尔玛强化成二级飓风，并在几乎同一时间达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]155公里的最高强度，再于行进至马萨诸塞州[[南塔克特|南塔克特]]东南偏东约130公里海域时减弱成一级飓风。<ref name="HURDAT" />受[[加拿大大西洋省份|加拿大大西洋省份]]上空的[[高气压|高气压天气系统]]影响，气旋转向[[罗盘方位|东南偏东]]<ref name="mwr" />，于8月30日降级成热带风暴，并且当天就在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]最西南角的东南偏南方向约290公里洋面转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref name="HURDAT" />。8月31日至9月2日，阿尔玛的残留在高气压天气系统影响下以环形路线移动<ref name="mwr" />。9月2日晚，这些残留蜿蜒向东北前进，最终在[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]南面逐渐消散<ref name="HURDAT" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Alma_1962_rainfall.png|thumb]]

发展成阿尔玛前，东风波就在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]降下暴雨，该岛东南部发生洪灾<ref name="stormdata" />。8月25日，系统又在阿尔玛成形前一天令佛罗里达州和乔治亚州大西洋海域波涛汹涌，促使气象机构向[[戴通纳海滩|戴通纳海滩]]至[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]发布小型船只警告<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | page = 2 | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | date = 1962-08-25 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=r8NPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vlIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3457,1810201&hl=en | title = Tropical Storm May Be Brewing | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | archive-date = 2022-01-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220116054558/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=r8NPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vlIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3457%2C1810201&hl=en }}</ref>。此外，佛罗里达州和乔治亚州还有部分地区降下小雨<ref name="rainfall">{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | date = 2009-09-28 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | title = Hurricane Alma – August 25–31, 1962 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002430/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alma1962.html | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alma1962.html }}</ref>。气旋沿美国东岸平行移动期间，气象部门建议南卡罗莱纳州[[埃迪斯托岛_(南卡罗莱纳州)|埃迪斯托岛]]（{{lang|en|Edisto Island}}）至[[里特河_(南卡罗莱纳州)|里特河]]（{{lang|en|Little River}}）河口的小型船只留在港内不要出海<ref>{{cite report | author = J. A. Cummings | date = 1962-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200805025031/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/local/hlschs.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/local/hlschs.gif | title = Special News Bulletin | work = Weather Bureau Office Charleston, South Carolina | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | archivedate = 2020-08-05 }}</ref>。该州沿海部分地区降下暴雨并伴有强烈阵风，但没有报导表明当地因此受到破坏<ref name="stormdata" />。

虽然飓风的移动路线距陆地很近，但北卡罗莱纳州[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]][[纳格斯黑德_(北卡罗莱纳州)|纳格斯黑德]]（{{lang|en|Nags Head}}）所测最强阵风时速也只达到85公里<ref name="mwr" />。阵风将[[哈特拉斯_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈特拉斯]]（{{lang|en|Hatteras}}）的一根电线杆刮倒，导致全镇三分之一地区停电一小时<ref>{{cite report | author = Weddle | publisher = National Hurricane Center | work = Weather Bureau Office Cape Hatteras, North Carolina | date = 1962-08-28 | title = The Passage of Tropical Storm Alma at WBO Cape Hatteras NC on August 28, 1962 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051755/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshhat.gif | accessdate = 2013-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshhat.gif | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。哈特拉斯出现0.91米的风暴潮，导致一定程度的[[海蚀|侵蚀]]<ref name="mwr" />。全美以哈特拉斯角降水最多，达264毫米<ref name="rainfall" />。北卡罗莱纳州的损失数额约为3.5万美元<ref name="mwr" />。阿尔玛的[[风眼|风眼]]从弗吉尼亚海角（{{lang|en|Virginia Capes}}）东南偏南约110公里海域经过，[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]东部降下小雨并有阵风，沿海地区还出现大浪。全州以[[诺福克_(弗吉尼亚州)|诺福克]]雨量最高，但也只有16毫米，所以没有发生洪灾。[[汉普顿锚地|汉普顿锚地]]有0.4米的风暴潮，引发轻度海滩侵蚀。该州以[[亨利角|亨利角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Henry}}）所测持续风速最强，为每小时58公里，但没有造成显著破坏<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061101/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshorf.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshorf.gif | title = Report on Tropical Storm Alma August 27 and 28, 1962 | author = Sachse | date = 1962-08-28 | work = Weather Bureau Office Norfolk, Virginia | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | format = GIF | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

风暴的外围雨带导致马萨诸塞州几乎连续降雨40小时，并伴有持续数小时的强烈阵风。降雨总量达到76毫米，但新英格兰此时正遭受旱灾袭击，这些降水整体利大于弊。<ref name="stormdata" />降雨致使路面湿滑，引发多起交通事故<ref name="bos">{{cite report | author = Edward Sable, Boston Weather Bureau Airway Station | date = 1962-09-12 | title = Summary of Tropical Storm Alma | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/bos1107c.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/bos1107c.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。马萨诸塞州出现0.6米高的风暴潮，引起轻度沿海洪灾，还有上百艘船被阿尔玛产生的大浪摧毁<ref name="mwr" />。此外，尚有包括游艇在内的许多小型船只挣脱锚固并撞上岩石。气旋在[[波士顿|波士顿]]产生时速82公里的北向阵风，马萨诸塞州沿海地区风速达到每小时97公里。<ref>{{cite report | author = Tenenbaum | work = Boston Weather Bureau Airway Station | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1962-08-30 | title = Preliminary Report on Hurricane Alma | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshbos.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120302215513/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshbos.gif | archivedate = 2012-03-02 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>大风刮倒许多树木，导致部分地区停电，电话服务中断，[[林恩_(马萨诸塞州)|林恩]]还有一幢房屋和旁边所停的汽车被砸毁。风雨交加下，[[米德尔塞克斯县_(马萨诸塞州)|米德尔塞克斯县]][[梅尔罗斯_(马萨诸塞州)|梅尔罗斯]]（{{lang|en|Melrose}}）民防设施内的[[民防警报|警报器]]因短路而持续报警超过两小时。[[艾塞克斯县_(马萨诸塞州)|艾塞克斯县]][[托普斯费尔德_(马萨诸塞州)|托普斯费尔德]]（{{lang|en|Topsfield}}）的展览馆内有一顶大帐篷被风刮倒。<ref name="bos" />风暴在[[黑弗里尔_(马萨诸塞州)|黑弗里尔]]间接引发一起卡车打滑撞人事故，导致一名女子丧生<ref>{{cite news | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1bQrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7f4FAAAAIBAJ&pg=6192,5224179&dq=hurricane+alma&hl=en | title = Alma Heads Away From N.E. Coastline | date = 1962-08-30 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = The Telegraph | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | archive-date = 2022-01-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220116054647/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1bQrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7f4FAAAAIBAJ&pg=6192%2C5224179&dq=hurricane+alma&hl=en }}</ref>。

飓风在新英格兰其他多地产生降水，[[罗得岛州|罗得岛州]]沿海地区的风速达到每小时97公里。北面远至[[新罕布什尔|新罕布什尔]][[朴次茅斯_(新罕布什尔州)|朴次茅斯]]都因气旋影响受到破坏，<ref name="bos" />降雨范围则向北延伸至[[缅因州|缅因州]]境内<ref name="rainfall" />。整场风暴在新英格兰造成的经济损失不足100万美元<ref name="mwr" />。

